1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 38 =

20
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:37,260
The other day,
Fan proposed eight measures for Shaanxi,

21
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:40,340
including canceling military fields,

22
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,060
drilling wells to bury dead people

23
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,580
and relieving refugees in Shaanxi.

24
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:45,260
I reviewed them.

25
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:46,420
Today,

26
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:49,100
I’d like to discuss about teaching military books.

27
00:01:57,500 --> 00:02:00,660
Scholars only honor passing the imperial exam.

28
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:03,980
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
So, few people in Directorate of Education

29
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,220
are good at martial arts.

30
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:08,620
At the border, some soldiers have martial arts

31
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:09,820
and are familiar with border affairs,

32
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,980
but they haven’t read military books

33
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:13,260
and don’t know how to be good generals.

34
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:15,180
I don’t think

35
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:18,220
we need a separate department for martial arts.

36
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:21,540
If some scholars enjoy military books

37
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:24,940
or some border soldiers are smart,

38
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,660
we can pick a few of them

39
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:29,580
and teach them military books and strategies.

40
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,260
In this case, maybe some of them

41
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:34,860
will become competent generals.

42
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:41,260
Not to mention if this measure can be taken,

43
00:02:42,020 --> 00:02:44,380
Fan is at least generous enough

44
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:45,780
to care for our nation,

45
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:48,460
without partiality for literature or martial arts.

46
00:02:49,380 --> 00:02:52,500
You should take him as an example.

47
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,580
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

48
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,140
I’ve something else to tell you, Your Majesty.

49
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:03,380
Go ahead.

50
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:06,420
If you think

51
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:08,620
some of the measures I’ve proposed

52
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,540
can be taken...

53
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:12,060
Such measures

54
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:14,740
haven’t been tried at the border yet.

55
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:16,500
I thought about them carefully.

56
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:19,180
But they still couldn’t be perfect

57
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:21,660
and must be corrected in time.

58
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:26,420
So, I’d like to go to Shaanxi personally

59
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,820
for inspection and supervision.

60
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:39,540
I’ll think about it carefully.

61
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:49,740
Deputy Officer Yang, please kindly

62
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:51,660
announce the edict.

63
00:03:51,820 --> 00:03:53,260
Get up, Mrs. Xue.

64
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:56,260
I’m not ordered to come here.

65
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:58,780
I’m just out for some business

66
00:03:58,820 --> 00:04:00,700
and get you to the palace for Madam Zhang.

67
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:02,420
She feels bored,

68
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:04,900
and wants you to talk with her.

69
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:14,260
Why is there grass and mud on you?

70
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:17,700
Have you rolled

71
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:19,260
on the grass?

72
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,140
He pounced on me first.

73
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:23,940
She was crafty.

74
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:26,940
I caught her, but she wanted to cheat.

75
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,660
You’re getting more voluble.

76
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:32,260
Why is here a pimple?

77
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:34,820
Can it be an insect bite?

78
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:39,460
A mosquito bite. I feel a bit itchy.

79
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,340
Why don’t you go get me some ointment?

80
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:50,660
After she was deceased,

81
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:54,020
I felt my heart broken.

82
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,260
I had wanted to die with her.

83
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:59,540
But when I woke up this morning,

84
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:02,740
I saw His Majesty stare at me,

85
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:06,020
sad,

86
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:08,620
distressed

87
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:11,460
and scared.

88
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:14,460
Just like I was scared

89
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,340
when Chuyue was badly ill.

90
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:18,540
So, I swore to myself that

91
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:22,060
I must get better.

92
00:05:24,300 --> 00:05:26,300
I can’t make him as sad as I was.

93
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:29,300
His Majesty cares for you the most.

94
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:30,780
You know that.

95
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:33,860
So, even for his sake,

96
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:35,900
you must get better soon.

97
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:38,820
So, today,

98
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,540
I take medicine regularly

99
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:43,500
and try to have more food.

100
00:05:44,980 --> 00:05:46,380
I even invite you for a talk.

101
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:52,420
I’m so envious of you.

102
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:55,220
Your husband remarried you.

103
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,620
But you’re the only wife

104
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:57,780
he has.

105
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:01,700
However sad he feels for your sister,

106
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:04,380
he’s getting nicer to you.

107
00:06:05,460 --> 00:06:07,460
And you have your own children.

108
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:12,100
My husband is too stubborn.

109
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:14,820
I’m afraid what he’s doing

110
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:18,660
will bring him great misfortune.

111
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:49,820
The proposal from Deputy Censor Wang Gongchen,

112
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:52,060
says everything about

113
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:54,980
= Let’s talk about Teng abusing public expenses. =
my wisdom and benevolence.

114
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:59,420
He pretends to be mad at home, disheveled.

115
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:02,340
He’s forcing me.

116
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:05,420
He’s forcing me to punish him

117
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:06,500
and kill him.

118
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:10,020
He’s forcing me to be an unworthy man

119
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:10,940
against ancestral rules.

120
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,780
He’s forcing me to be a fatuous emperor.

121
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:25,820
Pick it up.

122
00:07:29,140 --> 00:07:30,660
I can’t just kill him.

123
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:36,260
Do you think he’s not afraid of death?

124
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:40,980
He just knows I can’t severely punish him.

125
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:43,340
Trapped in

126
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:44,940
the moral high ground of benevolence,

127
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:47,140
I have to watch him make a scene.

128
00:07:49,060 --> 00:07:49,740
Your Majesty.

129
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:53,580
Manager Zhang Maoze asked to see you.

130
00:07:53,773 --> 00:07:54,700
Get him in.

131
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,340
Zuixinglai was all right this morning.

132
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:01,180
I watched him eat two stuffed buns

133
00:08:01,180 --> 00:08:01,980
and a dish of pickles

134
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,500
before I went to help Her Highness

135
00:08:03,540 --> 00:08:04,660
with the banquet in a couple of days.

136
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:06,260
When I came back at dusk,

137
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:08,020
I found him a bit listless with no appetite.

138
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:09,540
I coaxed him into having some food.

139
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:11,260
But he threw up one hour later.

140
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,380
After he lay in bed, he threw up twice again.

141
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,220
I wonder if he has a heatstroke.

142
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,820
So, I want you to check on him.

143
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:22,420
After I heard of the rumor,

144
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:23,540
I checked on that

145
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:25,020
and tracked down to

146
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:27,020
the letters of collusion for treason.

147
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:29,140
But as far as I see,

148
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:30,860
Shi Jie is a mere scholar.

149
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:32,340
Fu Bi isn’t a powerful official.

150
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,700
They have no adherents, either.

151
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:37,260
Meanwhile, they’re receiving favor from you.

152
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,060
The rumor goes that

153
00:08:39,180 --> 00:08:41,020
they’re going to force you to abdicate

154
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:42,620
and support a new emperor.

155
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:45,780
It makes no sense at all.

156
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:52,340
We found the letters

157
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:54,580
Shi Jie wrote to Fu Bi.

158
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:57,660
We determined it’s

159
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:58,540
Shi Jie’s handwriting.

160
00:08:58,780 --> 00:08:59,580
But we haven’t found

161
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:01,380
any arrangements for treason yet.

162
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,260
I can keep investigating on it.

163
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:05,580
If they really want to do something,

164
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,260
I think we’ll find it out.

165
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:09,820
I don’t need you

166
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:12,300
to confirm

167
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:13,900
if Shi Jie wants to rebel.

168
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:17,100
Even if he wants,

169
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:19,340
he isn’t powerful enough.

170
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:23,380
You want me to check out who started the rumor?

171
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:24,740
It’s easy to find out, too.

172
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:27,020
Why do we bother to

173
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:28,940
find out such an easy truth?

174
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:40,420
Some royal officials turn out to make a scene.

175
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:44,900
Some obedient officials turn out to play tricks.

176
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:48,220
Are they afraid of punishment?

177
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:51,740
They have the support from ancestral rules,

178
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,100
the nation and the people.

179
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:54,300
That’s all I care.

180
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:55,980
They’re not afraid of me at all.

181
00:09:56,540 --> 00:09:59,180
They’re pushing me.

182
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:11,020
Your Majesty.

183
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:17,580
Ask the Cabinet to draft a decree.

184
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:21,340
Fan Zhongyan are insightful to propose

185
00:10:21,340 --> 00:10:22,380
the eight measures for Shaanxi

186
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:24,980
and they will be very helpful.

187
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,980
He’ll be sent to Shaanxi

188
00:10:28,580 --> 00:10:29,780
for inspection.

189
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:34,380
Teng Zongliang was slightly punished

190
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:37,900
when he was demoted for abusing public funds.

191
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:42,980
Get him demoted again
and banished to Yueyang, Yuezhou.

192
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:46,700
Then,

193
00:10:50,340 --> 00:10:52,060
let Fu Bi and Shi Jie know that.

194
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:55,580
Yes, Your Majesty.

195
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:33,900
I can’t mess up with them.

196
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:37,380
I...

197
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,700
I don’t understand too much.

198
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:43,300
= Liang Huaiji =
From the books I read,

199
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:45,060
I know

200
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:46,980
wise emperors of dynasties

201
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:48,420
and ancestors of our nation

202
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:50,420
have a lot of scruples

203
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,860
and they don’t mess up with officials.

204
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:04,980
All right.

205
00:12:08,100 --> 00:12:09,980
I coax shrewish officials.

206
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:13,700
I pretend not to know tricks they make.

207
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:16,260
I must protect those

208
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:18,220
who work for me,

209
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:20,460
whether they’re obedient or not.

210
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:25,860
Huaiji, you’re wrong.

211
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:29,500
Not only wise emperors have scruples.

212
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:33,980
Every emperor who doesn’t want to lose his nation

213
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:38,260
has scruples in his heart.

214
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:44,226
It’s late.

215
00:12:44,310 --> 00:12:46,513
Don’t bother to copy them.

216
00:12:47,130 --> 00:12:48,550
I’m going to see Madam Zhang.

217
00:12:49,576 --> 00:12:50,783
Go to Pavilion of Phoenix

218
00:12:50,853 --> 00:12:52,523
and send some toys

219
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:54,023
to Zuixinglai and Huirou.

220
00:13:05,460 --> 00:13:06,300
Huaiji, listen.

221
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:08,340
Is there a flying cricket?

222
00:13:14,780 --> 00:13:17,700
Sorry, Your Majesty, I don’t know.

223
00:13:19,420 --> 00:13:20,700
Why do you apologize again?

224
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:22,420
It doesn’t matter.

225
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:28,220
Last month in Pavilion of Phoenix,

226
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:30,500
Zuixinglai saw Huirou’s painting.

227
00:13:31,180 --> 00:13:32,700
He said that was a common cricket.

228
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:34,620
But Huirou told him

229
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:35,940
it was a flying cricket.

230
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:38,820
A bit different from a common cricket.

231
00:13:39,420 --> 00:13:41,340
But it chirps more beautifully.

232
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:43,060
Zuixinglai wanted

233
00:13:43,180 --> 00:13:44,980
to catch a living flying cricket right away.

234
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,180
But that day,

235
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:47,580
he failed to recite the poem

236
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:48,740
and had to copy it for ten times.

237
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:50,300
He couldn’t go.

238
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,140
So, Your Majesty,

239
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:55,860
the insect toy you ask me to take to little prince

240
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:58,860
that can move and chirp...

241
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:00,460
That’s a flying cricket?

242
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:04,620
I asked the skilled craftsmen

243
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:07,380
with Directorate of Astronomy

244
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:09,300
to make it specially for him.

245
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,100
It moves and chirps.

246
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,140
But don’t tell him

247
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,780
I specially make him

248
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:15,940
such a valuable thing.

249
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:17,100
Tell him

250
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:18,780
I just saw it in the storehouse

251
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:20,060
and give it to him for fun.

252
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:25,620
Oh, I see.

253
00:14:26,700 --> 00:14:28,740
You care for little prince

254
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:30,300
and want to make him happy.

255
00:14:30,780 --> 00:14:32,860
But you must pretend to be very serious

256
00:14:33,620 --> 00:14:35,420
in case he’s spoilt

257
00:14:35,740 --> 00:14:37,020
and can’t rule the nation after growing up.

258
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:40,020
You’ve worked for me for years.

259
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:41,420
You’ve learnt

260
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,140
more than what a local official has learnt

261
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:44,100
after working for two or three years.

262
00:14:45,260 --> 00:14:46,540
But you’ve never

263
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:48,380
changed your mind.

264
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,460
I’m right about you.

265
00:14:53,060 --> 00:14:53,820
Huaiji.

266
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:55,540
I’ve told Ren Shouzhong to

267
00:14:55,540 --> 00:14:56,540
get you promoted.

268
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:57,940
Pick a fine day

269
00:14:57,940 --> 00:14:59,220
and you’ll move to Pavilion of Phoenix,

270
00:14:59,260 --> 00:15:01,700
taking care of Zuixinglai.

271
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:10,940
What? You don’t like it?

272
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:14,060
I...

273
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:15,980
I like it.

274
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:17,700
I will

275
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:18,940
take good care of little prince.

276
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:21,020
I...

277
00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:22,060
I understand.

278
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,940
I know you’re a loyal boy.

279
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:26,020
That’s why I ask you

280
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:27,900
to stay with my son.

281
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:30,180
You shall care for him and defend him.

282
00:15:30,660 --> 00:15:33,020
Sometimes you shall exhort him, too.

283
00:15:36,180 --> 00:15:37,100
Yes, Your Majesty.

284
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:55,380
Why does he have an even higher temperature

285
00:15:55,380 --> 00:15:56,340
than he did one hour ago?

286
00:15:57,300 --> 00:15:58,740
He isn’t having a heatstroke.

287
00:15:59,380 --> 00:16:00,460
The prince is honorable.

288
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:02,420
I think

289
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:03,580
the Head should be asked

290
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,820
to check on him.

291
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:14,020
I know

292
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:16,340
I shouldn’t have mentioned the politics.

293
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:18,580
But I still want to have a try.

294
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:21,340
All the other ladies

295
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,820
listen to Her Highness.

296
00:16:23,340 --> 00:16:25,300
Only Mrs. Xue gets on well with me.

297
00:16:26,540 --> 00:16:27,740
She has dinner with me

298
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:29,780
and makes me delicious snacks.

299
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:32,260
I’ve been feeling depressed lately.

300
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:34,140
So I ask her to come and stay with me.

301
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:37,980
If you kill Wang Gongchen,

302
00:16:37,980 --> 00:16:39,380
she would certainly die, too.

303
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:42,580
Then I’ll lose my only friend.

304
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:45,660
When has any official been killed?

305
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:50,820
If you banish him from the Capital

306
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:52,740
to somewhere barren,

307
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,460
Mrs. Xue can’t

308
00:16:55,460 --> 00:16:56,980
often come to me, either.

309
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:02,660
Your Majesty, I’m begging you.

310
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:04,460
Don’t punish Deputy Censor Wang.

311
00:17:04,900 --> 00:17:05,620
Look.

312
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,740
He reported honestly,

313
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:09,660
for the good of our nation.

314
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:12,020
Besides,

315
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:13,500
maybe...

316
00:17:14,220 --> 00:17:16,420
maybe Fan Zhongyan showed partiality.

317
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:17,500
Ouyang Xiu has been

318
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:18,780
framing Deputy Censor Wang up.

319
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:19,780
And Teng Zongliang...

320
00:17:19,780 --> 00:17:20,540
He hasn’t been cleared of

321
00:17:20,540 --> 00:17:22,260
abusing public funds.

322
00:17:23,100 --> 00:17:24,940
The demotion isn’t a serious punishment.

323
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:32,220
Your Majesty?

324
00:17:36,860 --> 00:17:37,620
Bihan.

325
00:17:38,020 --> 00:17:39,900
You don’t know politics. Don’t talk nonsense.

326
00:17:42,340 --> 00:17:43,580
I’m not talking about politics.

327
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:44,700
I just want to

328
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:45,980
plead for Mrs. Xue’s husband.

329
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,740
You want me to practice favoritism?

330
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:57,380
He will not leave the Capital.

331
00:17:57,700 --> 00:17:58,540
Don’t worry.

332
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:03,220
You shall no longer talk about politics

333
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:05,460
or ask for partiality for anyone else.

334
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:09,100
Do you mean you won’t punish him?

335
00:18:11,100 --> 00:18:12,060
Didn’t I say?

336
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:13,380
He won’t leave the Capital.

337
00:18:16,060 --> 00:18:17,220
If you feel bored,

338
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:19,260
feel free to bring Mrs. Xue here.

339
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:21,060
But you must promise me

340
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:22,940
to stop worrying

341
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:24,540
and get healthy.

342
00:18:31,900 --> 00:18:32,660
What’s wrong?

343
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:34,380
Why are you crying?

344
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:38,100
I know I’m making things difficult for you.

345
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:39,580
Unexpectedly,

346
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:42,460
you didn’t scold me,

347
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:43,980
but complied with my request.

348
00:18:46,420 --> 00:18:49,820
As you said,

349
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:53,220
Wang Gongchen is a loyal official.

350
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:57,380
He won’t leave the Capital, anyway.

351
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:58,860
But you shall

352
00:18:59,540 --> 00:19:01,340
no longer talk about politics.

353
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:06,300
You like Mrs. Xue.

354
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:07,900
Ask her to come and make you happy.

355
00:19:08,180 --> 00:19:09,940
Then you’ll get better soon.

356
00:19:13,100 --> 00:19:14,100
Don’t worry, Your Majesty.

357
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:15,940
Now I believe that

358
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:17,780
you truly care for me.

359
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:20,820
I will get better

360
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:23,620
and stay with you all my life.

361
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:25,500
I won’t leave you,

362
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:26,500
whatever happens.

363
00:19:44,380 --> 00:19:45,140
Sir.

364
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:47,740
His fever is brought down a little.

365
00:19:48,100 --> 00:19:49,620
And he’s sleeping soundly.

366
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:51,340
Is he all right?

367
00:19:52,380 --> 00:19:53,180
Madam Miao.

368
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:57,620
We had a consultation after checking on him.

369
00:19:58,580 --> 00:20:02,780
We think little prince has pathogenic heat.

370
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:07,020
After taking some medicine to relieve heat,

371
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:09,660
he’s getting better as expected.

372
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:12,380
Lusi.

373
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:16,420
No. No. No.

374
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:20,340
Madam Miao, little prince is too young

375
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:22,180
and he’s suddenly ill.

376
00:20:23,740 --> 00:20:25,460
He had a rather high fever just now.

377
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:27,700
Though he’s getting better,

378
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:32,380
I’m afraid he’ll get worse at night.

379
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:36,220
Please give us some bamboo mats.

380
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:38,460
We’re going to stay overnight,

381
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:40,100
guarding him.

382
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:43,900
Go get them.

383
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:56,980
Get back to sleep.

384
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,060
I’m not hot.

385
00:20:58,260 --> 00:20:59,340
I’ll wait here

386
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:01,100
until Zuixinglai gets better.

387
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:02,900
I’m not sleepy. Princess.

388
00:21:03,020 --> 00:21:03,980
I’m not sleepy at all.

389
00:21:07,020 --> 00:21:07,700
Princess.

390
00:21:09,316 --> 00:21:11,260
- Princess. - Huaiji, what brings you here?

391
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:12,980
Father knows that Zuixinglai is ill?

392
00:21:15,020 --> 00:21:17,340
His Majesty asked me to bring some toys

393
00:21:17,340 --> 00:21:18,500
to you and little prince.

394
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:22,380
What? the prince is ill?

395
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:27,180
Nonsense.

396
00:21:27,900 --> 00:21:28,980
= Shi Jie, courtesy name Shoudao =
Nonsense!

397
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:31,620
I admire His Majesty so much.

398
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:34,180
How would I ever rebel?

399
00:21:34,340 --> 00:21:35,500
How would I?

400
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:37,940
Someone is framing me up.

401
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:39,620
That’s it.

402
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:41,140
I’ll refute!

403
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:44,780
Who is framing me up?

404
00:21:45,140 --> 00:21:47,420
Who is he on earth?

405
00:21:51,100 --> 00:21:53,940
= Fu Bi’s Wife Yan Qingsu =
Someone must be trying to

406
00:21:53,940 --> 00:21:55,660
kill you and Mr. Shi.

407
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:58,740
His Majesty is wise.

408
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:01,620
He won’t be deceived, will he?

409
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:08,100
But an emperor is always suspicious.

410
00:22:08,780 --> 00:22:09,820
Will His Majesty

411
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:12,500
have a grudge against you?

412
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:19,860
Darling.

413
00:22:21,340 --> 00:22:23,260
Do Mr. Fan and Mr. Han know this?

414
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:25,620
Shall I

415
00:22:26,260 --> 00:22:28,060
go and discuss with father

416
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:29,540
for some instructions?

417
00:22:32,060 --> 00:22:34,980
No. I’m going directly to the palace

418
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:36,300
and meet Her Highness.

419
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:37,140
Qingsu.

420
00:22:41,020 --> 00:22:42,020
You’re showing His Majesty and other officials

421
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:44,940
how I can gang up.

422
00:22:46,660 --> 00:22:47,460
In the imperial court,

423
00:22:48,300 --> 00:22:50,060
my good friends are important officials.

424
00:22:50,940 --> 00:22:54,860
At home, my father-in-law is a minister.

425
00:22:57,020 --> 00:22:58,540
My wife often goes to the palace

426
00:22:59,620 --> 00:23:01,340
and gets on well the Empress,

427
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:02,500
the ruler of the imperial harem.

428
00:23:12,620 --> 00:23:13,580
In this way,

429
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:15,940
seems like

430
00:23:16,660 --> 00:23:17,380
I’m truly capable of

431
00:23:17,380 --> 00:23:18,700
forcing the Emperor.

432
00:23:22,100 --> 00:23:22,780
What...

433
00:23:23,820 --> 00:23:26,180
What should we do then?

434
00:23:34,060 --> 00:23:35,900
Mr. Fan has defended Teng Zongliang

435
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:37,300
and saved him.

436
00:23:38,380 --> 00:23:41,020
However, those who are against the reform

437
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:42,780
hate him more.

438
00:23:50,820 --> 00:23:51,900
Mr. Fan said,

439
00:23:53,100 --> 00:23:54,260
in more than one year since the reform,

440
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:55,860
half of redundant officials have been fired.

441
00:23:56,180 --> 00:23:57,340
It’s a kind of success.

442
00:23:58,300 --> 00:24:00,060
The war has ceased.

443
00:24:00,860 --> 00:24:02,180
It’s time to build a stable society

444
00:24:02,340 --> 00:24:03,660
and develop agriculture and business.

445
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:07,740
We’re yet trying to exterminate evil officials

446
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:09,820
and get rid of corruption.

447
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:11,860
This action

448
00:24:12,820 --> 00:24:14,340
will certainly bring risks.

449
00:24:15,420 --> 00:24:16,340
These guys

450
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:19,420
are mortally exaggerating such risks

451
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:20,820
and try to convince His Majesty.

452
00:24:33,060 --> 00:24:33,820
Darling.

453
00:24:36,900 --> 00:24:38,820
I shouldn’t have interfered

454
00:24:38,820 --> 00:24:39,980
with such an important thing.

455
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,540
Whatever you do,

456
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,940
I’ll just follow you.

457
00:24:47,380 --> 00:24:48,020
But...

458
00:24:49,220 --> 00:24:51,540
you’re framed up for treason.

459
00:24:53,060 --> 00:24:54,820
I only want you

460
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:55,820
to think of a retreat

461
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:58,780
for our children.

462
00:25:05,060 --> 00:25:06,620
Tomorrow, I’m going to apply

463
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:08,420
for leaving the Capital.

464
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:27,980
It was until now

465
00:25:28,980 --> 00:25:30,460
did I realize

466
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:32,500
the hatred and objection

467
00:25:34,460 --> 00:25:35,900
resulted from the complete removal
of maladministration.

468
00:25:38,300 --> 00:25:39,180
I don’t want

469
00:25:40,020 --> 00:25:42,700
the nation or the people to suffer, either.

470
00:25:57,980 --> 00:25:58,820
Huirou, look.

471
00:25:59,500 --> 00:26:02,340
What a nice bracelet and pendant!

472
00:26:03,540 --> 00:26:04,580
Aren’t they

473
00:26:04,580 --> 00:26:06,060
what you thought of

474
00:26:06,180 --> 00:26:07,660
when you learnt to draw maids last month?

475
00:26:08,820 --> 00:26:10,660
Your father said you draw the maid

476
00:26:10,900 --> 00:26:12,020
with a wrong specification.

477
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,860
In fact, he kept that in mind,

478
00:26:14,420 --> 00:26:15,700
had them forged

479
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:16,980
and sent to you.

480
00:26:18,020 --> 00:26:19,540
He didn’t.

481
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:22,060
According to Huaiji, father said

482
00:26:22,620 --> 00:26:24,340
a senior eunuch found them accidentally

483
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:25,780
when he was cleaning

484
00:26:26,220 --> 00:26:27,380
the storehouse.

485
00:26:29,140 --> 00:26:30,580
Since your father said so,

486
00:26:30,740 --> 00:26:31,900
let it be.

487
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:33,700
But what a coincidence!

488
00:26:34,300 --> 00:26:35,300
What you like

489
00:26:35,340 --> 00:26:36,500
and what Zuixinglai likes,

490
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:38,580
you have them easily

491
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:39,700
when someone searches the storehouse.

492
00:26:40,940 --> 00:26:42,420
But Zuixinglai is sick.

493
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:44,660
He just said he missed father.

494
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:46,740
Why didn’t you ask Huaiji

495
00:26:46,740 --> 00:26:47,780
to tell father

496
00:26:47,860 --> 00:26:48,860
and bring him here?

497
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:57,460
Your father is busy with business.

498
00:26:58,620 --> 00:27:00,780
Her Highness gave an order

499
00:27:01,580 --> 00:27:03,420
and the head of physicians has come.

500
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:05,700
Zuixinglai is better.

501
00:27:07,860 --> 00:27:08,660
Besides...

502
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,740
Besides, father is in the Pavilion of Luan.

503
00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:15,580
Huaiji didn’t tell us.

504
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:17,540
But everyone in the palace knows that.

505
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:18,940
In recent months,

506
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,620
father has taken the Pavilion of Luan

507
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:21,500
as his own palace.

508
00:27:21,900 --> 00:27:22,980
Watch your tongue, Huirou.

509
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:24,980
It’s not

510
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:25,860
what you should say.

511
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:30,100
Madam.

512
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:31,620
Couches and snacks for physicians

513
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:32,460
are ready.

514
00:27:37,740 --> 00:27:38,540
Huaiji.

515
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:41,380
Tonight, the head of physicians will stay

516
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:42,580
with another two physicians.

517
00:27:42,980 --> 00:27:44,060
I’m going there.

518
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:47,580
Why don’t you stay with Huirou?

519
00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:50,340
Aye.

520
00:28:06,420 --> 00:28:07,260
Don’t go.

521
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:11,420
You can’t fall asleep.

522
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:13,980
I’ll go get some soothing incense.

523
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:16,420
Don’t go, brother.

524
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:23,060
Princess, you mustn’t call me like that.

525
00:28:24,140 --> 00:28:25,060
Brother.

526
00:28:36,620 --> 00:28:38,580
Why don’t you close your eyes?

527
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:40,220
I’m not leaving.

528
00:28:42,620 --> 00:28:45,300
If I close my eyes,

529
00:28:45,660 --> 00:28:47,700
I can’t feel you around.

530
00:28:52,900 --> 00:28:54,940
When you close your eyes,

531
00:28:56,220 --> 00:28:57,820
I can still talk with you.

532
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:10,780
Huaiji, why did you come and work at the palace?

533
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:16,420
Because my family is poor.

534
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:19,420
What does poor mean?

535
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:25,420
It means

536
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:28,700
we don’t have any money.

537
00:29:31,020 --> 00:29:32,980
But I don’t have much money, either.

538
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:34,780
Every day,

539
00:29:34,820 --> 00:29:36,580
mother only gives me twelve coppers.

540
00:29:37,460 --> 00:29:39,140
If I lose it in playing the game,

541
00:29:39,580 --> 00:29:41,060
she won’t give me any.

542
00:29:41,820 --> 00:29:43,100
If I win,

543
00:29:43,660 --> 00:29:45,020
she’ll give all my money

544
00:29:45,180 --> 00:29:46,820
to whoever plays with me.

545
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:50,260
I have no money at last.

546
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:52,460
I’m also poor, aren’t I?

547
00:29:55,220 --> 00:29:56,740
No, princess.

548
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:02,700
Being poor means having little to eat or wear.

549
00:30:03,740 --> 00:30:06,060
You may not even have any rice.

550
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,820
You’ll only eat sweet potatoes every day.

551
00:30:10,620 --> 00:30:12,340
But sweet potatoes taste good.

552
00:30:13,100 --> 00:30:14,060
Once I was hungry,

553
00:30:14,620 --> 00:30:16,300
you got me a sweet potato in the kitchen

554
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,100
and that tasted the best.

555
00:30:18,940 --> 00:30:20,620
I’m going to have sweet potatoes every day.

556
00:30:23,540 --> 00:30:24,380
For example,

557
00:30:25,860 --> 00:30:27,140
if you have something,

558
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,580
but others don’t.

559
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:31,180
And they are in urgent need of it.

560
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,460
They’re poor,

561
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:35,780
compared with you.

562
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:39,460
Look.

563
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:42,020
You have many beautiful clothes.

564
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:43,460
But your maids don’t have

565
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:44,780
what you have.

566
00:30:45,540 --> 00:30:46,500
It means

567
00:30:47,340 --> 00:30:49,580
they’re poorer than you.

568
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:53,780
I kind of understand.

569
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:57,940
Others have many clothes

570
00:30:58,420 --> 00:30:59,420
and sweet potatoes,

571
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:02,620
but your family didn’t have

572
00:31:02,620 --> 00:31:04,140
so many clothes

573
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:06,780
or sweet potatoes for you.

574
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:10,100
They had to send you here.

575
00:31:13,540 --> 00:31:14,540
Sort of.

576
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:17,460
I see.

577
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:19,380
Qiuhe is poorer than me.

578
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:22,060
Because I have much free time,

579
00:31:23,020 --> 00:31:25,660
but she’s working every day.

580
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:28,140
She barely has her own time.

581
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:31,620
Madam Yu is poorer than mother.

582
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:35,140
Because mother is a senior concubine.

583
00:31:35,980 --> 00:31:38,340
But Madam Yu is inferior.

584
00:31:39,100 --> 00:31:41,900
She has less monthly pay

585
00:31:42,060 --> 00:31:43,260
and fewer festival rewards.

586
00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:45,900
What about

587
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:49,820
Madam Zhang and Her Highness?

588
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:53,980
Which one of them is poorer?

589
00:31:55,820 --> 00:31:58,180
Madam Zhang wants to be the Empress.

590
00:31:58,700 --> 00:31:59,740
But she isn’t.

591
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:03,380
Once she wanted the red umbrella on her sedan

592
00:32:03,860 --> 00:32:05,980
which is used by the Empress,

593
00:32:06,900 --> 00:32:08,940
and also wanted as many guards

594
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:10,140
as the Empress,

595
00:32:11,100 --> 00:32:14,300
officials scolded her.

596
00:32:16,220 --> 00:32:17,580
But father often

597
00:32:17,580 --> 00:32:19,060
visits Madam Zhang.

598
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:23,580
Recently, he even goes there every day.

599
00:32:25,340 --> 00:32:28,060
Madam Zhang has lost Yaoyao.

600
00:32:28,820 --> 00:32:31,460
But Her Highness doesn’t have any child yet.

601
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:36,260
So, Her Highness is poorer.

602
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:45,380
Get to sleep, princess.

603
00:32:48,740 --> 00:32:49,460
Forget it.

604
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:51,620
Madam Zhang is very poor, too.

605
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:54,900
Her daughters died.

606
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:58,020
Father is poor, too.

607
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:00,660
Officials don’t let father do

608
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,460
what he wants to do.

609
00:33:07,740 --> 00:33:08,940
I can’t mess up with them.

610
00:33:10,940 --> 00:33:12,620
Huaiji, you’re wrong.

611
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:16,340
Not only wise emperors have scruples.

612
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:21,420
Every emperor who doesn’t want to lose his nation

613
00:33:22,620 --> 00:33:25,700
has scruples in his heart.

614
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:51,300
How is Zuixinglai now?

615
00:33:51,540 --> 00:33:52,460
His fever is gone.

616
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:53,860
But he gets more listless.

617
00:33:54,140 --> 00:33:55,900
He had porridge this morning, but brought it up.

618
00:33:57,380 --> 00:33:58,780
Your Highness. Madam Miao.

619
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:02,620
Last night, His Majesty asked Huaiji

620
00:34:02,620 --> 00:34:03,580
to bring Huirou and Zuixinglai

621
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:04,740
some toys.

622
00:34:05,140 --> 00:34:06,660
I was staying with Zuixinglai

623
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:07,820
and settling down the physicians.

624
00:34:08,260 --> 00:34:09,460
Huirou was worried, too.

625
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:11,340
I asked Huaiji to stay with her overnight.

626
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:15,940
How is His Majesty lately?

627
00:34:16,180 --> 00:34:17,260
He is fine.

628
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:19,700
But he’s too busy with national affairs.

629
00:34:20,180 --> 00:34:21,620
He reviews proposals and meets officials

630
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:22,700
until eight o’clock every day.

631
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:28,020
You always stay with His Majesty

632
00:34:28,100 --> 00:34:29,180
when he reviews proposals.

633
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:31,620
You don’t need to take care of his living.

634
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:34,220
But when His Majesty is working,

635
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:35,700
you should pay more attention

636
00:34:36,180 --> 00:34:37,820
if he’s tired or thirty.

637
00:34:38,620 --> 00:34:40,380
Liaozi and the other are very careful.

638
00:34:40,980 --> 00:34:43,060
If His Majesty keeps working

639
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:44,460
for two hours,

640
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:46,380
they’ll try to

641
00:34:46,380 --> 00:34:48,380
bring some tea, snacks and fruit

642
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,940
or have a chat with him.

643
00:34:53,660 --> 00:34:55,180
His Majesty is right about you.

644
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:58,500
Your Highness. Madam Miao.

645
00:34:58,980 --> 00:35:00,100
I’ve got something to say.

646
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:17,540
You look much better today.

647
00:35:18,580 --> 00:35:19,700
I think

648
00:35:20,020 --> 00:35:21,220
you’ll recover soon.

649
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:24,620
Since I thought it through,

650
00:35:26,420 --> 00:35:27,700
I feel much better.

651
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:31,100
His Majesty cares for me.

652
00:35:32,420 --> 00:35:33,700
I must recover soon,

653
00:35:34,580 --> 00:35:35,940
even for his sake.

654
00:35:39,620 --> 00:35:40,900
That would be nice.

655
00:35:42,500 --> 00:35:45,820
Forget all the unhappy

656
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:47,300
and sad things.

657
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:48,900
And we will...

658
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:49,660
I can’t forget that.

659
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:54,060
I won’t, either.

660
00:35:56,220 --> 00:35:57,260
My daughter

661
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:00,860
is my precious treasure.

662
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:04,300
I won’t let her die for nothing.

663
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:10,380
The maid who saw Yaoyao have an attack

664
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:11,780
and ran away,

665
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:14,300
I will find her,

666
00:36:15,620 --> 00:36:16,780
find out what happened

667
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:20,620
and I will skin her.

668
00:36:24,500 --> 00:36:25,220
Aunt.

669
00:36:28,420 --> 00:36:29,700
Go tell my uncle,

670
00:36:30,620 --> 00:36:31,700
Wang Gongchen,

671
00:36:32,260 --> 00:36:33,180
and Chief Xia.

672
00:36:34,420 --> 00:36:35,140
Tell them.

673
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:37,980
If anyone of them

674
00:36:37,980 --> 00:36:39,380
finds that good-for-nothing outside the palace,

675
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,300
I swear

676
00:36:42,940 --> 00:36:44,180
I will try my best

677
00:36:44,180 --> 00:36:45,140
to get him high position and wealth.

678
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,300
Go ask a physician to check on Huirou.

679
00:37:15,260 --> 00:37:16,020
Your Highness.

680
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,380
I had the pimple yesterday.

681
00:37:17,660 --> 00:37:18,940
I guess it was some sort of

682
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:19,740
insect bite.

683
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:21,380
It itched.

684
00:37:21,620 --> 00:37:22,860
But it was okay later.

685
00:37:23,460 --> 00:37:24,260
This morning,

686
00:37:24,260 --> 00:37:25,740
when the maid combed my hair,

687
00:37:26,020 --> 00:37:27,980
Huaiji was nervous when he saw it.

688
00:37:30,420 --> 00:37:31,740
You’re a girl.

689
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:34,060
If a bite isn’t healed,

690
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:36,500
it’s bad to have a scar.

691
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:38,460
It’s careful of Huaiji.

692
00:38:10,700 --> 00:38:12,500
Your Highness, you’re experienced.

693
00:38:12,620 --> 00:38:13,900
I guess you’ve realized

694
00:38:14,340 --> 00:38:17,100
it’s not a bite of any common insect,

695
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:18,260
but the tick.

696
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:21,580
I’ll ask someone to fetch appliances

697
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:23,700
from the Imperial Hospital

698
00:38:23,820 --> 00:38:25,100
to get the tick out and kill it.

699
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:27,660
Off you go.

700
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:40,100
Fu Bi sounds reasonable.

701
00:38:41,460 --> 00:38:42,540
I also think

702
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:45,300
Khitan is at daggers drawn with Xixia.

703
00:38:45,860 --> 00:38:47,460
They won’t attack Dai’er people

704
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,740
with Xixia.

705
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:51,900
If we station troops on the border hastily,

706
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:54,580
we’ll fall for the trick.

707
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:58,820
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

708
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:01,700
I quite agree with

709
00:39:02,140 --> 00:39:03,140
the eight measures proposed by Fan.

710
00:39:04,060 --> 00:39:05,700
I thought about it carefully last night.

711
00:39:06,180 --> 00:39:08,620
A lot waits to be done after the end of the war.

712
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:11,660
We really need to send a capable official there

713
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:12,860
who is honest, loyal and persistent

714
00:39:13,060 --> 00:39:14,220
with rich experience in

715
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:15,220
governing the border.

716
00:39:15,780 --> 00:39:16,700
After thinking about it carefully,

717
00:39:17,060 --> 00:39:19,580
I think Fan is the best candidate.

718
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:25,860
You make sense, Your Majesty.

719
00:39:26,180 --> 00:39:28,300
= Su Shunqin, courtesy name Zimei =
But Minister Fan takes care of

720
00:39:28,540 --> 00:39:30,460
many state affairs.

721
00:39:31,060 --> 00:39:32,060
If he’s suddenly transferred,

722
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:35,180
I’m afraid state affairs might be affected.

723
00:39:35,460 --> 00:39:36,140
Your Majesty.

724
00:39:36,620 --> 00:39:39,220
I quite agree with Su Shunqin.

725
00:39:39,820 --> 00:39:43,020
There is always an order of priority.

726
00:39:43,940 --> 00:39:45,300
The reform...

727
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:49,180
The...

728
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:00,820
Yes, there is always an order of priority.

729
00:40:01,460 --> 00:40:02,820
But for a large nation,

730
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:04,540
there must be a foundation and a roof.

731
00:40:05,740 --> 00:40:08,780
The peace of the border is the foundation.

732
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:10,100
If our nation isn’t in peace,

733
00:40:10,540 --> 00:40:11,900
how can we carry on with the reform?

734
00:40:14,740 --> 00:40:16,740
Aye, Your Majesty.

735
00:40:17,060 --> 00:40:17,700
Xiwen.

736
00:40:17,740 --> 00:40:20,180
I won’t let you down, Your Majesty.

737
00:40:29,260 --> 00:40:30,340
In recent months,

738
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:31,940
disasters happen frequently in Hebei.

739
00:40:32,780 --> 00:40:34,820
A loyal and capable official

740
00:40:35,060 --> 00:40:36,140
should go there for inspection.

741
00:40:36,860 --> 00:40:40,060
Fu Bi, you’ve been to Khitan several times

742
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,420
to defend our nation.

743
00:40:41,780 --> 00:40:43,900
You enjoy a high prestige in border provinces.

744
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:45,420
Would you like to go?

745
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:50,380
Aye, Your Majesty.

746
00:40:53,140 --> 00:40:54,660
I’m afraid there’s disturbance in disasters.

747
00:40:54,860 --> 00:40:55,860
The problem shall be solved immediately.

748
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:57,300
I’d like to go with light luggage
and few attendants

749
00:40:57,700 --> 00:40:59,860
early tomorrow morning.

750
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:11,420
Has Deputy Censor Wang Gongchen come?

751
00:41:14,020 --> 00:41:14,740
Yes.

752
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:16,980
= Jia Changchao, courtesy name Ziming =
But he didn’t dare to come in.

753
00:41:17,900 --> 00:41:20,500
He’s waiting outside until being summoned.

754
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:24,900
Didn’t dare to come in?

755
00:41:28,460 --> 00:41:30,460
He abandoned his uniform

756
00:41:30,780 --> 00:41:32,900
and showed his aspiration with a hunger strike.

757
00:41:33,460 --> 00:41:34,620
What else is he afraid of?

758
00:41:36,300 --> 00:41:38,580
Your Majesty, will...

759
00:41:38,860 --> 00:41:40,340
If he’s properly dressed today,

760
00:41:40,380 --> 00:41:41,300
get him in.

761
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:24,860
Is she all right

762
00:42:24,860 --> 00:42:25,940
after the tick is pulled out?

763
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,620
Are there still other ticks?

764
00:42:28,140 --> 00:42:28,900
Madam.

765
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:30,620
Lusi and I checked

766
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:32,500
all over the princess.

767
00:42:32,620 --> 00:42:33,620
No more ticks are found.

768
00:42:35,180 --> 00:42:36,180
Is it toxic?

769
00:42:37,140 --> 00:42:39,220
The tick sucks blood,

770
00:42:39,420 --> 00:42:42,260
and meanwhile injects toxin into human body.

771
00:42:42,420 --> 00:42:44,460
It was just like the anesthetic.

772
00:42:45,340 --> 00:42:47,700
So, the princess didn’t feel anything.

773
00:42:48,460 --> 00:42:49,940
With the toxin in the body,

774
00:42:50,140 --> 00:42:51,420
people feel differently.

775
00:42:51,980 --> 00:42:54,180
Some might be badly ill.

776
00:42:55,020 --> 00:42:57,820
Some might only ache for days.

777
00:42:58,340 --> 00:42:59,300
Is Zuixinglai all right?

778
00:42:59,500 --> 00:43:01,100
We both rolled on the grass.

779
00:43:03,860 --> 00:43:04,740
Go check carefully

780
00:43:04,740 --> 00:43:05,900
if there are any ticks on Zuixinglai.

781
00:43:06,500 --> 00:43:07,740
Skin behind his ears, on his head

782
00:43:08,620 --> 00:43:09,780
and even the private parts.

783
00:43:10,820 --> 00:43:12,220
Check if there are any ticks on him too.

784
00:43:14,020 --> 00:43:14,740
Aye.

785
00:43:28,180 --> 00:43:37,860
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

786
00:43:39,180 --> 00:43:47,540
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

787
00:43:50,380 --> 00:43:55,100
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

788
00:43:56,060 --> 00:44:00,220
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

789
00:44:01,660 --> 00:44:07,140
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

790
00:44:07,140 --> 00:44:11,940
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

791
00:44:15,620 --> 00:44:21,260
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

792
00:44:21,260 --> 00:44:26,140
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

793
00:44:26,660 --> 00:44:32,420
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

794
00:44:32,420 --> 00:44:37,500
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

795
00:44:37,940 --> 00:44:42,860
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

796
00:44:43,500 --> 00:44:48,340
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

797
00:44:49,020 --> 00:44:54,180
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

798
00:44:54,660 --> 00:44:59,700
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

799
00:45:00,260 --> 00:45:04,340
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

800
00:45:05,780 --> 00:45:10,420
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

801
00:45:11,460 --> 00:45:16,620
♪ The howling wind ♪

802
00:45:16,980 --> 00:45:21,060
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

803
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:27,460
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

804
00:45:28,100 --> 00:45:33,340
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

805
00:45:33,740 --> 00:45:39,020
♪ The howling wind ♪

806
00:45:39,340 --> 00:45:44,220
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

807
00:45:44,820 --> 00:45:51,540
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
